{"tid":704347,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 7 / 7 Plus 出現音效晶片鬆脫，維修費或需自付！","createTime":"2018-06-16T11:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T22:03:45.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2798b71b064f7be29762213e22deea228c34af65","tid":704347,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"叫人出iPhone 7都唔好出8嘅巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/06/15/iphone-7-sound-ic-issue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2Fiphone-7-sound-ic-issue%2F&d=QQpQzr8%2B%2FFnZQYpGTGtOG%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=a8437f8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/06/15/iphone-7-sound-ic-issue/</a><br />\n<br />\n最近關於 iPhone 7／7 Plus 的報導頻出，主要是涉及了 iPhone 7 / 7 Plus 出現音效晶片虛焊導致的種種問題。音效晶片虛焊導致的問題並不僅僅只是揚聲器，麥克風失效這麼簡單，更嚴重的是出現了手機啟動不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nApple 對此問題沒有什麼聲明，而大多數 iPhone 7 / 7 Plus 用戶的手機都已經過了保養期，如果 Apple 沒有給 iPhone 7 / 7 Plus 延保，那麼手機的維修費就只能自己掏錢包了。但如果你有技術的話，倒是不妨嘗試跟著YouTube 眾多的維修影片學習維修。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0f4f4db71ea6f82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F0f4f4db71ea6f82.jpg&h=299c84f7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n這次故障的原因在於音效晶片和輸入組件之間鏈接出現鬆動，根據 Tech Insights 的 iPhone 7 拆解照片來看，該音效晶片的左側出現了至少四點脫焊，出現問題的焊點一多，維修費用高達 100~150 美元左右。<br />\n<br />\n出現問題的原因是不是由於音效處理器而導致的呢？我們從音效處理器的型號開始研究。 iPhone 7 / 7 Plus 的故障音效解碼處理器的型號為 Apple / Cirrus Logic 338S00105，與 iPhone 6S 的一樣，只是將音效放大器更新為 Cirrus Logic 338S00220 。<br />\n<br />\niPhone 6S 並沒有出現過這個問題，那問題顯而易見，不是出於硬件了。只可能出於對質量的 QC 把控不足。希望 Apple 能夠及時認識到這個問題，給大眾一個好的答覆。"},{"pid":"d7c8f8d7d07f085cdc5f488f92d3b883cec9f393","tid":704347,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"對於mass的QC<br />\n<br />\nFuck that<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dfe23aaee1926ee6c7a119ce62b6811bc7ace1","tid":704347,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854caa68a3a56a2bb77c0f0df799e9e75e7d93b1","tid":704347,"uid":11589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"屌我呢掛部7plus有時打機用喇叭會長響沙聲，kill左apps都仲會響沙聲，要reboot先無事，唔知係咪呢個鬆脫問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f2eabc029b42778cb1a1c7669a2d20fc8c2bc8","tid":704347,"uid":22044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"凈係想知 8 係唔係一樣"},{"pid":"9fb9af06a43cff73d251c1b6c4429416662928e1","tid":704347,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T22:03:45.000Z","msg":"iPhone 8又贏"}]}